title: Financial Modeling & Fundraising Strategy for Venture X – A Corlax Wellness Green Energy Startup
description: We’re launching Venture X, a green energy startup under Corlax Wellness, and need a freelancer to build a professional financial model to support our fundraising efforts. The model should clearly articulate revenue streams, cost structures, and growth scenarios while highlighting the sustainability and market opportunity of our technology. The right partner will help us produce investor-ready materials that attract capital and inspire confidence.
